Switch the forked proto helpers to rules_proto providers.

The internal patch moves ProtoInfo, proto_common, and ProtoLangToolchainInfo loads away from com_google_protobuf and onto rules_proto so the Go proto rules keep working with the newer protobuf layout.

This port keeps the public rules_go proto surface unchanged and only updates the provider load sites inside the vendored fork.

